                <h1>Peel and Stick vs. Paste Wallpaper: Which Is Better?</h1>
                <p>Peel and stick wallpaper offers convenience and ease of installation, perfect for renters or DIY enthusiasts. It easily removes without damaging walls, while traditional paste wallpaper provides a classic finish and durability. However, the latter requires more skill and prep work. Choose based on your lifestyle and design needs.</p>
